data.name: syncOptionBox.ToolTip
data.value: This sets the behavior of the sync. Merge Prompt: This will ask you which contact to overwrite if both have been updated. Merge Outlook Wins: If both contacts have been updated, the Google contact will be overwritten. Merge Google Wins: If both contacts have been updated, the Outlook contact will be overwritten. Outlook To Google Only: Only updates Google contacts based on outlook contacts. Google To Outlook Only: Only updates Outlook contacts based on google contacts.
